public class ReplenishmentRequestDetail extends ReplenishmentRequest
The ReplenishmentRequestDetail class extends ReplenishmentRequest, providing additional details about the specific medicine and pharmacist involved in the request.

      Parameters:
      id - The unique ID of the replenishment request.
      medicine - The medicine associated with the replenishment request.
      pharmacist - The pharmacist who made the replenishment request.
      newAmount - The amount of medicine requested for replenishment.
      status - The current status of the replenishment request.
      createdAt - The date and time when the request was created.
      updatedAt - The date and time when the request was last updated.
